.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/discovery/session-resume-continuity-ladder.md:19:`session_resume` is the canonical recovery surface when hook-injected startup context is unavailable. The handler walks the documented continuity ladder for the target spec folder: `handover.md`, `_memory.continuity` frontmatter, then the canonical spec docs (`implementation-summary.md`, `tasks.md`, `plan.md`, `spec.md`).
