.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/tooling-and-scripts/completion-verdict-freshness-validation.md:26:The validation helper recomputes a normalized continuity fingerprint from packet content, compares it with `_memory.continuity.session_dedup.fingerprint`, and checks packet-scoped dirty paths. Clean recomputes pass; stale fingerprints warn unless enforcement is enabled. Clock-drift cases are recognized as pass conditions.
